data.expected_result: When you type # + some characters used in the channel name, two suggestions should pop up.
data.short_description: When two channels with the same name are created and you try to link to any one of the two channels in another channel in the server, only one channel shows up in channel suggestions.
data.steps_to_repro: - Create a channel - Create another channel with the same name in the same server. - Go to another channel in the server and type # and some characters used in the channel name (not the full channel name)
